        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><strong>No Bonuses in Bankruptcy Act of 2021</strong></p> <p>This bill prohibits debtors in bankruptcy proceedings from paying bonuses to certain individuals including insiders (such as relatives) and highly compensated employees. </p>]]>
        </text>
