      <item>
        <titleType>Official Title as Introduced</titleType>
        <title>To amend title 11 of the United States Code to prohibit the payment of bonuses to highly compensated individuals employed by the debtor and insiders of the debtor to perform services during the bankruptcy case, and for other purposes.</title>
      </item>
